Product.Name: Danusertib (PHA-739358)
Information: Danusertib (PHA-739358) is an Aurora kinase inhibitor for Aurora A/B/C with IC50 of 13 nM/79 nM/61 nM, modestly potent to Abl, TrkA, c-RET and FGFR1, and less potent to Lck, VEGFR2/3, c-Kit, CDK2, etc. Phase 2.

Product.Name: BMS-754807
Information: BMS-754807 is a potent and reversible inhibitor of IGF-1R/InsR with IC50 of 1.8 nM/1.7 nM, less potent to Met, Aurora A/B, TrkA/B and Ron, and shows little activity to Flt3, Lck, MK2, PKA, PKC etc. Phase 1/2.

Product.Name: AT9283
Information: AT9283 is a potent JAK2/3 inhibitor with IC50 of 1.2 nM/1.1 nM; also potent to Aurora A/B, Abl(T315I). Phase 1/2.

Product.Name: Regorafenib (BAY 73-4506)
Information: Regorafenib (BAY 73-4506) is a multi-target inhibitor for VEGFR1, VEGFR2, VEGFR3, PDGFRÎ², Kit, RET and Raf-1 with IC50 of 13 nM/4.2 nM/46 nM, 22 nM, 7 nM, 1.5 nM and 2.5 nM, respectively.

Product.Name: CUDC-101
Information: CUDC-101 is a potent multi-targeted inhibitor against HDAC, EGFR and HER2 with IC50 of 4.4 nM, 2.4 nM, and 15.7 nM, and inhibits class I/II HDACs, but not class III, Sir-type HDACs. Phase 1.

Product.Name: BX-912
Information: BX912 is a potent and specific PDK1 inhibitor with IC50 of 12 nM, 9- and 105- fold greater selectivity for PDK1 than PKA and PKC, respectively. In comparison to GSK3Î², selectivity for PDK1 is 600-fold.

Product.Name: AEE788 (NVP-AEE788)
Information: AEE788 is a potent inhibitor of EGFR and HER2/ErbB2 with IC50 of 2 nM and 6 nM, less potent to VEGFR2/KDR, c-Abl, c-Src, and Flt-1, does not inhibit Ins-R, IGF-1R, PKCÎ± and CDK1. Phase 1/2.

Product.Name: PF-573228
Information: PF-573228 is an ATP-competitive inhibitor of FAK with IC50 of 4 nM, ~50- to 250-fold selective for FAK than Pyk2, CDK1/7 and GSK-3Î².

Product.Name: LY2784544
Information: LY2784544 is a potent JAK2 inhibitor with IC50 of 3 nM, effective in JAK2V617F, 8- and 20-fold selective versus JAK1 and JAK3. Phase 2.

Product.Name: Degrasyn (WP1130)
Information: WP1130 (Degrasyn) is a selective deubiquitinase (DUB: USP5, UCH-L1, USP9x, USP14, and UCH37) inhibitor and also suppresses Bcr/Abl, also a JAK2 transducer (without affecting 20S proteasome) and activator of transcription (STAT).

Product.Name: Forskolin
Information: Forskolin is a ubiquitous activator of eukaryotic adenylyl cyclase (AC), commonly used to raise levels of cAMP in the study and research of cell physiology.

Product.Name: PP121
Information: PP-121 is a multi-targeted inhibitor of PDGFR, Hck, mTOR, VEGFR2, Src and Abl with IC50 of 2 nM, 8 nM, 10 nM, 12 nM, 14 nM and 18 nM, also inhibits DNA-PK with IC50 of 60 nM.

Product.Name: DCC-2036 (Rebastinib)
Information: DCC-2036 is a conformational control Bcr-Abl inhibitor for Abl1(WT) and Abl1(T315I) with IC50 of 0.8 nM and 4 nM, also inhibits SRC, LYN, FGR, HCK, KDR, FLT3, and Tie-2, and low activity to seen towards c-Kit. Phase 1/2.

Product.Name: GSK2126458 (GSK458)
Information: GSK2126458 is a highly selective and potent inhibitor of p110Î±/Î²/Î´/Î³, mTORC1/2 with Ki of 0.019 nM/0.13 nM/0.024 nM/0.06 nM and 0.18 nM/0.3 nM, respectively. Phase 1.

Product.Name: TG101209
Information: TG101209 is a selective JAK2 inhibitor with IC50 of 6 nM, less potent to Flt3 and RET with IC50 of 25 nM and 17 nM, ~30-fold selective for JAK2 than JAK3, sensitive to JAK2V617F and MPLW515L/K mutations.

Product.Name: Sotrastaurin
Information: Sotrastaurin is a potent and selective pan-PKC inhibitor, mostly for PKCÎ¸ with Ki of 0.22 nM; inactive to PKCÎ¶. Phase 1/2.

Product.Name: AZD4547
Information: AZD4547 is a novel selective FGFR inhibitor targeting FGFR1/2/3 with IC50 of 0.2 nM/2.5 nM/1.8 nM, weaker activity against FGFR4, VEGFR2(KDR), and little activity observed against IGFR, CDK2, and p38. Phase 1/2.

Product.Name: TAE226 (NVP-TAE226)
Information: NVP-TAE226 is a potent FAK inhibitor with IC50 of 5.5 nM and modestly potent to Pyk2, ~10- to 100-fold less potent against InsR, IGF-1R, ALK, and c-Met.

Product.Name: WHI-P154
Information: WHI-P154 is a potent JAK3 inhibitor with IC50 of 1.8 Î¼M, no activity against JAK1 or JAK2, also inhibits EGFR, Src, Abl, VEGFR and MAPK, prevents Stat3, but not Stat5 phosphorylation.

Product.Name: GW441756
Information: GW441756 is a potent, selective inhibitor of TrkA with IC50 of 2 nM, with very little activity to c-Raf1 and CDK2.

Product.Name: BAY 11-7082
Information: BAY 11-7082 is a NF-ÎºB inhibitor, inhibits TNFÎ±-induced IÎºBÎ± phosphorylation with IC50 of 10 Î¼M.

Product.Name: AZ20
Information: AZ20 is a novel potent and selective inhibitor of ATR kinase with IC50 of 5 nM, 8-fold selectivity over mTOR.

Product.Name: RKI-1447
Information: RKI-1447 is a potent inhibitor of ROCK1 and ROCK2, with IC50 of 14.5 nM and 6.2 nM, respectively, has anti-invasive and antitumor activities.

Product.Name: AZ191
Information: AZ191 is a potent and selective DYRK1B inhibitor with IC50 of 17 nM, about 5- and 110-fold selectivity over DYRK1A and DYRK2, respectively.

Product.Name: CEP-32496
Information: CEP-32496 is a highly potent inhibitor of BRAF(V600E/WT) and c-Raf with Kd of 14 nM/36 nM and 39 nM, also potent to Abl-1, c-Kit, Ret, PDGFRÎ² and VEGFR2, respectively; insignificant affinity for MEK-1, MEK-2, ERK-1 and ERK-2. Phase 1/2.
